<section class="section2" id="sec2">
    <h2 class="about-club-heading , headings" style="text-align: center; color: brown;" >&#x22C6 ABOUT CLUB &#x22C6</h2>
  <p class="about-club-pg">Welcome to The Binary Club—the heart of coding and technology at RKGIT Ghaziabad!<br>
    At The Binary Club, we are passionate about building a community where innovation, problem-solving, and coding excellence thrive. Our club is dedicated to empowering students with the tools and knowledge to succeed in the tech world, whether you're a coding novice or an experienced developer.
    Through a variety of events like hackathons, coding competitions, workshops, and collaborative projects, we aim to provide a platform where creativity meets logic, and ideas transform into reality. 
    <br>The Binary Club isn’t just about writing code; it’s about developing skills that last a lifetime—teamwork, leadership, and the perseverance to solve complex challenges.
    Join us as we explore the exciting world of programming, foster a spirit of innovation, and make a meaningful impact both within our college and beyond.<br><br><b> Code, Create, Innovate.</b><br><b> The Binary Club—Its all about 0’s & 1’s!</b>
   </p>
